### Register a viewer
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "viewer1",
  "password": "123456",
  "role": "viewer"
}

###

### Register an editor
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "editor1",
  "password": "123456",
  "role": "editor"
}

###

### Register an admin
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin1",
  "password": "123456",
  "role": "admin"
}

###

### Login as editor
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "editor1",
  "password": "123456"
}

###

### Create a blog (editor required)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/blogs?username=editor1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "First Blog by Editor",
  "content": "This blog is created by editor1"
}

###

### View all blogs (viewer, editor, admin can all do this)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/blogs?username=viewer1

###

### Update blog (only owner or admin)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/blogs/{{blogId}}?username=editor1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Blog Title",
  "content": "Editor updated their blog content"
}

###

### Delete blog (only owner or admin)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/blogs/{{blogId}}?username=editor1

###

### Admin deletes someone elseâ€™s blog
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/blogs/{{blogId}}?username=admin1
